lue><Style><FontFamily>Arial</FontFamily><FontSize>8pt</FontSize></Style></TextRun></TextRuns><Style /></Paragraph><Paragraph><TextRuns><TextRun><Value>Insured will be insured for accidental death benefit in the amount of 100% (one hundred percent) of Sum Insured. When Dai-ichi Life issues the</Value><Style><FontFamily>Arial</FontFamily><FontSize>8pt</FontSize></Style></TextRun></TextRuns><Style /></Paragraph><Paragraph><TextRuns><TextRun><Value>Insurance Certificate, the Temporary Insurance Coverage will cease,  and all the Insurance Benefits as specified in this Policy and/or Rider's Terms</Value><Style><FontFamily>Arial</FontFamily><FontSize>8pt</FontSize></Style></TextRun></TextRuns><Style /></Paragraph><Paragraph><TextRuns><TextRun><Value>and Conditions commence from the Policy Commencement Date. If Dal-ichi Life postpones the processing of, or rejects the insurance application, </Value><Style><FontFamily>Arial</FontFamily><FontSize>8pt</FontSize></Style></TextRun></TextRuns><Style /></Paragraph><Paragraph><TextRuns><TextRun><Value>the Temporary  Insurance Coverage will expire immediately. </Value><Style><FontFamily>Arial</FontFamily><FontSize>8pt</FontSize></Style></TextRun></TextRuns><Style /></Paragraph><Paragraph><TextRuns><TextRun><Value /><Style><FontFamily>Arial</FontFamily><FontSize>8pt</FontSize></Style></TextRun></TextRuns><Style /></Paragraph></Paragraphs><rd:DefaultName>Textbox4</rd:DefaultName><Top>5.22737cm</Top><Height>2.008cm</Height><Width>18.7cm</Width><ZIndex>4</ZIndex><Style><Border><Style>None</Style></Border><PaddingLeft>2pt</PaddingLeft><PaddingRight>2pt</PaddingRight><PaddingTop>2pt</PaddingTop><PaddingBottom>2pt</PaddingBottom></Style></Textbox><Textbox Name="Textbox5"><KeepTogether>true</KeepTogether><Paragraphs><Paragraph><TextRuns><TextRun><Value>?????????????????????????????????????????????????????????</Value><Style><FontFamily>Khmer OS Siemreap</FontFamily><FontSize>8pt</FontSize></Style></TextRun><TextRun><Value xml:space="preserv