</Value><Style><FontFamily>Khmer OS Siemreap</FontFamily><FontSize>8pt</FontSize></Style></TextRun></TextRuns><Style /></Paragraph></Paragraphs><rd:DefaultName>Textbox5</rd:DefaultName><Top>8.79114cm</Top><Height>3.56973cm</Height><Width>18.7cm</Width><ZIndex>7</ZIndex><Style><Border><Style>None</Style></Border><PaddingLeft>2pt</PaddingLeft><PaddingRight>2pt</PaddingRight></Style></Textbox><Textbox Name="Textbox8"><KeepTogether>true</KeepTogether><Paragraphs><Paragraph><TextRuns><TextRun><Value>This Temporary Insurance Coverage benefits will not be paid if any of the following occur, whether direct or indirect, result in the death of the Life</Value><Style><FontFamily>Arial</FontFamily><FontSize>8pt</FontSize></Style></TextRun></TextRuns><Style /></Paragraph><Paragraph><TextRuns><TextRun><Value>Insured:</Value><Style><FontFamily>Arial</FontFamily><FontSize>8pt</FontSize></Style></TextRun></TextRuns><Style /></Paragraph><Paragraph><TextRuns><TextRun><Value>    a.  Suicide, regardless of the mental condition of the Life Insured; or</Value><Style><FontFamily>Arial</FontFamily><FontSize>8pt</FontSize></Style></TextRun></TextRuns><Style /></Paragraph><Paragraph><TextRuns><TextRun><Value>    b.  Use of drugs, stimulants or alcohol violating the current law of Cambodia; or</Value><Style><FontFamily>Arial</FontFamily><FontSize>8pt</FontSize></Style></TextRun></TextRuns><Style /></Paragraph><Paragraph><TextRuns><TextRun><Value>    c.  Criminal acts committed by the Policy Owner, the Life Insured, or the Beneficiaries; or </Value><Style><FontFamily>Arial</FontFamily><FontSize>8pt</FontSize></Style></TextRun></TextRuns><Style /></Paragraph><Paragraph><TextRuns><TextRun><Value>    d.  The event of accident resulting in the death of the Life Insured occurs before the commencement of the temporary Insurance coverage</Value><Style><FontFamily>Arial</FontFamily><FontSize>8pt</FontSize></Style></TextRun></TextRuns><Style /></Paragraph><Paragraph><TextRuns><TextRun><Value>         period.</Value><Style><FontFamily>Arial</FontFamily><FontSize>8pt</FontSize></Style></TextRun></TextRuns><Style /></Paragraph><Paragraph><TextRuns><TextRun><Value>Instead, Dai-ichi Life will return all the paid Premiums to the Policy Owner.</Value><Style><FontFamily>Arial</FontFamily><FontSize>8pt</FontSize></Style></TextRun></TextRuns><Style /></Paragraph><Paragraph><TextRuns><TextRun><Value /><Style><FontFamily>Arial</FontFamily><FontSize>8pt</FontSize></Style></TextRun></TextRuns><Style /></Paragraph></Paragraphs><rd:DefaultName>Textbox4</rd:DefaultName><Top>12.36086cm</Top><Height>2.69186cm</Height><Width>18.7cm</Width><ZIndex>8</ZIndex><Style><Border><Style>None</Style></Border><PaddingLeft>2pt</PaddingLeft><PaddingRight>2pt</PaddingRight><PaddingTop>2pt</PaddingTop></Style></Textbox><Textbox Name="Textbox9"><KeepTogether>true</KeepTogether><Paragraphs><Paragraph><TextRuns><TextRun><Value>?????????????????</Value><Style><FontFamily>Khmer OS Siemreap</FontFamily><FontSize>8pt</FontSize><FontWeight>Bold</FontWeight></Style></TextRun><TextRun><Value xml:space="preserve"> </Value><Style><FontFamily>Kh Siemreap</FontFamily><FontSize>8pt</FontSize></Style></TextRun><TextRun><Value>?????????????????????????????</Value><Style><FontFamily>Khmer OS Siemreap</FontFamily><FontSize>8pt</FontSize><FontWeight>Normal</FontWeight></Style></TextRun><TextRun><Value xml:space="preserve"> </Value><Style><FontFamily>Kh Siemreap</FontFamily><FontSize>8pt</FontSize></Style></TextRun><TextRun><Value>?????????????????????</Value><Style><FontFamily>Khmer OS Siemreap</FontFamily><FontSize>8pt</FontSize><FontWeight>Normal</FontWeight></Style></TextRun><TextRun><Value xml:space="preserve"> </Value><Style><FontFamily>Kh Siemreap</FontFamily><FontSize>8pt</FontSize></Style></TextRun><TextRun><Value>????????????????????</Value><Style><FontFamily>Khmer OS Siemreap</FontFamily><FontSize>8pt</FontSize><FontWeight>Normal</FontWeight></Style></TextRun><TextRun><Value xml:space="preserve"> </Value><St